{"tid":323710,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"痔瘡痛到仆街，求救","createTime":"2017-07-15T20:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T18:32:14.000Z","uid":11484,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"19edab35f33da6f0c8f5666c89b6a5646cd8f412","tid":323710,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T20:23:27.000Z","msg":"有咩飲食方法可以減輕痛楚....<br />\n利申我係痛到連野都唔想食"},{"pid":"aec451908230c7c7c4221d129b3912f350610940","tid":323710,"uid":116341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T20:25:12.000Z","msg":"飲多d水最重要，要食菜但唔可以食太多，太多纖維痾果時好痛"},{"pid":"960575f423788ca980126b4de9762dcff69038b3","tid":323710,"uid":116341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T20:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲多d水最重要，要食菜但唔可以食太多，太多纖維痾果時好痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好食熱氣野，辣野是基本，食多d蕉排便順暢d冇咁痛"},{"pid":"a1523f6a3fd5ebfda3629a564cbf9a2d7ca89740","tid":323710,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T20:26:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96c78cad8256361068eb206976a038583ae2921a","tid":323710,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T20:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲多d水最重要，要食菜但唔可以食太多，太多纖維痾果時好痛</blockquote><br />\n平時我都有<br />\n但平時係完全冇感覺<br />\n但今日突然痛到仆街"},{"pid":"3c9e9d15689dec036f8eefbeee5e576c6d56ec1a","tid":323710,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T20:34:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩飲食方法可以減輕痛楚....<br />\n利申我係痛到連野都唔想食</blockquote><br />\n你D痔瘡生係個口到?</blockquote><br />\n痛到坐立不安<br />\n然後就直頭唔想食野"},{"pid":"80d6c5cf4ca64e3af214597a2c4240f5aa1b35c9","tid":323710,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T23:17:18.000Z","msg":"藥房買anusol ointment<br />\n外用<em></em>"},{"pid":"4861bf5e4e3098cef039a51de509afa4159fc5e2","tid":323710,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:34:48.000Z","msg":"想問飲羅漢果水得唔得"},{"pid":"75de161c803962d0c89fb7a076a619fe752a0201","tid":323710,"uid":60365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T03:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藥房買anusol ointment<br />\n外用<em></em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用一晚即刻搞掂，萬寧屈臣都有"},{"pid":"f8057e3cef283ee3a26386ad0ae2e1378c00b15f","tid":323710,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"做手術割左佢"},{"pid":"3382d42cd61ec7b27454fb71c7cfc7ce9e6a269b","tid":323710,"uid":32260,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"認真，搽藥膏時<br />\n用啲綿花，上滿啲藥膏<br />\n再推入屎眼入面<br />\n效果會好過就咁搽<br />\n唔洗膽心會拎唔返<br />\n因為你一痾屎佢就出返黎<br />\n<br />\n利申，複合痔 10 年，堅持唔做手術"},{"pid":"5ea127f4dbc9f312656e04bf15bd1c44dfffdc24","tid":323710,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>藥房買anusol ointment<br />\n外用<em></em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用一晚即刻搞掂，萬寧屈臣都有</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4i9m32cx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4i9m32cx&h=28fb4ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇醫生都係開呢隻, 喏係藥房買過$38/盒, 如果樓主話痛到抽筋, 冇用, 要食消炎藥"},{"pid":"ca8ea173f4795850cc39ad30f9f9165874279fc9","tid":323710,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:03:42.000Z","msg":"買個呢隻水坐墊, 冇咁壓住個pat pat<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gedt04bq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgedt04bq&h=94ab0286&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5ba89742cadbb81c8677c2b788239ac1df511f3","tid":323710,"uid":128555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:12:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩飲食方法可以減輕痛楚....<br />\n利申我係痛到連野都唔想食</blockquote><br />\n睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"45d308ea0dbc4bfbe5474ff4f5aff95664f08797","tid":323710,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"多謝各位<br />\n我睇下有冇上面隻藥塞賣先"},{"pid":"ee33dfa163d8b00b0c3d3e3053b9d92553bb238a","tid":323710,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:15:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩飲食方法可以減輕痛楚....<br />\n利申我係痛到連野都唔想食</blockquote><br />\n睇醫生啦</blockquote><br />\n聽朝一早去旅行<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"e74182d002024dd945aad15eb3cea8cd572831b3","tid":323710,"uid":127466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>藥房買anusol ointment<br />\n外用<em></em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用一晚即刻搞掂，萬寧屈臣都有</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4i9m32cx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4i9m32cx&h=28fb4ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇醫生都係開呢隻, 喏係藥房買過$38/盒, 如果樓主話痛到抽筋, 冇用, 要食消炎藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過, 呢隻無撚用. 用過幾盒除左止痕, 止痛外, 粒痔瘡無變化. 反而呢隻馬應龍真係好堅, 見粒痔瘡真係越縮越細 (有D女用黎縮眼袋 ). 華潤堂有但貴, 成 4x 支, 大陸買先10蚊支左右, 用兩星期開始會 feel 到粒野縮細左. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fungwah.com.hk/Product/Skin/Product2/image1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fungwah.com.hk%2FProduct%2FSkin%2FProduct2%2Fimage1.jpg&h=78e46ba9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81d3a0191cb98b4b651ad1fb68e5a5078bbd2e59","tid":323710,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:08:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>藥房買anusol ointment<br />\n外用<em></em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用一晚即刻搞掂，萬寧屈臣都有</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4i9m32cx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4i9m32cx&h=28fb4ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇醫生都係開呢隻, 喏係藥房買過$38/盒, 如果樓主話痛到抽筋, 冇用, 要食消炎藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過, 呢隻無撚用. 用過幾盒除左止痕, 止痛外, 粒痔瘡無變化. 反而呢隻馬應龍真係好堅, 見粒痔瘡真係越縮越細 (有D女用黎縮眼袋 ). 華潤堂有但貴, 成 4x 支, 大陸買先10蚊支左右, 用兩星期開始會 feel 到粒野縮細左. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fungwah.com.hk/Product/Skin/Product2/image1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fungwah.com.hk%2FProduct%2FSkin%2FProduct2%2Fimage1.jpg&h=78e46ba9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我已經買左<br />\n試下先"},{"pid":"ce7a52fd89cdde0522a0b4ebeb47abffb78cd73b","tid":323710,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"塞左兩日，雖然冇咁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但感覺仲係好腫好脹"},{"pid":"4031534b7012f45f514f2212b565aeec26e85d3a","tid":323710,"uid":10816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>塞左兩日，雖然冇咁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但感覺仲係好腫好脹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你應該係柯到屎眼突左出黎<br />\n腫到痛<br />\n<br />\n柯完沖涼用手推返入去<br />\n就唔痛<br />\n<br />\n醫生話呢世都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚴重先要做開刀手術....<br />\n<br />\n以後食野要注意, 要令到便便軟身d, 唔好咁大力柯<br />\n唔係出血似女人M黎咁<br />\n<br />\n利申: 做過來橡根扎小手術, 但無用, 札完忍唔到即柯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da1ac3cbbf4d59a7db7477f1ba494878df5b928","tid":323710,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:10:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>塞左兩日，雖然冇咁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但感覺仲係好腫好脹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你應該係柯到屎眼突左出黎<br />\n腫到痛<br />\n<br />\n柯完沖涼用手推返入去<br />\n就唔痛<br />\n<br />\n醫生話呢世都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚴重先要做開刀手術....<br />\n<br />\n以後食野要注意, 要令到便便軟身d, 唔好咁大力柯<br />\n唔係出血似女人M黎咁<br />\n<br />\n利申: 做過來橡根扎小手術, 但無用, 札完忍唔到即柯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢係塞入去，行兩步路自己走番出黎<br />\n呢d情況係咪搵醫生割左佢好d"},{"pid":"06b2f93381c826abbbd840a0241c14a332ad7ade","tid":323710,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:13:45.000Z","msg":"我明白果種痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瞓喺床都痛到流眼淚，莫講話行路<br />\n唯有浸藥/塞藥/食止痛無限loop<br />\n要成個禮拜先至無咁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得keep住食大量菜同生果"},{"pid":"f408b468f7bb89b775b6ef8c301ff6c2b9fc9f3c","tid":323710,"uid":10816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T00:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>塞左兩日，雖然冇咁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但感覺仲係好腫好脹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你應該係柯到屎眼突左出黎<br />\n腫到痛<br />\n<br />\n柯完沖涼用手推返入去<br />\n就唔痛<br />\n<br />\n醫生話呢世都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚴重先要做開刀手術....<br />\n<br />\n以後食野要注意, 要令到便便軟身d, 唔好咁大力柯<br />\n唔係出血似女人M黎咁<br />\n<br />\n利申: 做過來橡根扎小手術, 但無用, 札完忍唔到即柯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢係塞入去，行兩步路自己走番出黎<br />\n呢d情況係咪搵醫生割左佢好d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下夜晚柯完沖涼<br />\n再塞返入去<br />\n洗乾淨d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先去訓<br />\n我去睇政府普通科<br />\n醫生開藥塞同藥膏<br />\n兩樣一齊用黎消腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後要好小心柯屎咪咁大力<br />\n<br />\n真係好嚴重就割啦<br />\n好影響日常生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ac0c14ed80640a517954522d927dc521db63bc","tid":323710,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"去割啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ee7241246de77d489c1a37fd8f5f4a8c379813","tid":323710,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:32:08.000Z","msg":"其實有左之後係咪冇得縮番到0?<br />\n即係永遠都會凸少少只係冇咁明顯?<br />\n不過唔痛就當好番咁解?？"}]}